### 测试飞书 API 查询

### 1. 获取 Access Token
POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "app_id": "YOUR_APP_ID",
  "app_secret": "YOUR_APP_SECRET"
}

### 2. 查询记录 (使用 trackingIds)
POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps/X3hVw8dUTilgKQkACsCcOcaEnsg/tables/tblpWzxXOfwlZMHr/records/search
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filter": {
    "conjunction": "or",
    "conditions": [
      {
        "field_name": "追踪ID",
        "operator": "is",
        "value": ["FB-20260307-297"]
      }
    ]
  },
  "page_size": 100
}
